<L>__{exterior cornwall island woods, old casino night}
<A>__{ray and lila bounce through the woods to a collapsed building. an old black suv pulls up from the opposite direction, facing them. two middle aged chinese men, get out of the back. one carries an envelope. at the sight of ray and lila, he stops and says something to the other one. both turn around and head back to the suv. the driver jacques bruno, a large quebecois man, wearing a full length fur coat gets out. they argue. he pulls out a long pistol and motions the men to the acclaim.}
<C>__{ray}
<D>__{what the hell is he doing?}
<A>__{ray reaches for her gun.}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{keep that thing down.}
<A>__{bruno walks towards the acclaim.}
<C>__{lila }
<D>__{roll down the window and see what he wants.}
<C>__{ray}
<D>__{what the hell is going on here?}
<C>__{lila}
<D>__{just roll it down.}
<A>__{bruno stands at ray's window. ray slides the gun under her leg and rolls down the window. bruno hands her a tim horton's bag. she takes it.}
<C>__{bruno}
<P>__{(quebec french accent)}
<D>__{d'ey don't like de women driver.}
<A>__{he hands ray the envelope of cash.}
